data.name: RobustFast_checkBox.ToolTip
data.value:
Camera switching methods: Fast: Uncheck both. Fastest and uses least resources, may cause issues on some systems Robust: Check robust, uncheck Keep active. Saves resources, slower switch mechanism. Keep Active: Keeps both cameras live (which may be problematic in itself); doesn't attempt to swith cameras, needs more USB and system resources.
Best and most reliable method is unfortunately system dependent.
